    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2373440/extras/5e4ced7cee38eadc2d1996f55c5dd2e0.avif?t=1771500911\" width=620 height=75 /></span><br>将最佳武器与复杂符文词汇的力量结合，提升你的技能并击败强大的敌人。每一场战斗都是展示你机智和优化装备，为迎接等待你的挑战做好准备的机会。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2373440/extras/fd96d12c7d8d9d1bce6b2c2bf772d11f.poster.avif?t=1771500911\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2373440/extras/fd96d12c7d8d9d1bce6b2c2bf772d11f.webm?t=1771500911\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2373440/extras/fd96d12c7d8d9d1bce6b2c2bf772d11f.mp4?t=1771500911\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2373440/extras/851b27e8033155ee50961c3fde18ca7d.avif?t=1771500911\" width=620 height=75 /></span><br>通过共同经历难以置信的冒险结交终身的朋友。参加公会的战斗，如与龙的战斗或充满挑战的地下城，合作是获胜的关键！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2373440/extras/1c2f237dbdf7439d2c5237e668cbf8fa.poster.avif?t=1771500911\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2373440/extras/1c2f237dbdf7439d2c5237e668cbf8fa.webm?t=1771500911\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2373440/extras/1c2f237dbdf7439d2c5237e668cbf8fa.mp4?t=1771500911\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2373440/extras/59042b7821d5ed060fa84f5cf9e39b27.avif?t=1771500911\" width=620 height=75 /></span><br>在开放市场发现商人精神，这是一个充满活力的地方，玩家可以交换装备和其他资源。创造游戏经济，通过明智的决策致富。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2373440/extras/17601cb3a4578a24347c49cf73c29a3b.poster.avif?t=1771500911\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2373440/extras/17601cb3a4578a24347c49cf73c29a3b.webm?t=1771500911\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2373440/extras/17601cb3a4578a24347c49cf73c29a3b.mp4?t=1771500911\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2373440/extras/fef6a6278d4d357165115d12170dd899.avif?t=1771500911\" width=620 height=75 /></span><br>从与首领的史诗战斗中暂时休息，沉浸在村庄生活中。从事平静的耕作或钓鱼，沉浸在大自然的美丽中。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2373440/extras/443c8f5a64ec2aec012199f9d15dd484.poster.avif?t=1771500911\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2373440/extras/443c8f5a64ec2aec012199f9d15dd484.webm?t=1771500911\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2373440/extras/443c8f5a64ec2aec012199f9d15dd484.mp4?t=1771500911\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2373440/extras/a3e6f2062ff0dd483fc35fa8f2d88fa3.avif?t=1771500911\" width=620 height=75 /></span><br>Miners Settlement 的独特像素艺术图形邀请你踏上美丽冒险之旅。体验更新的图形并参观迷人的地点 - 从绿色的精灵森林到神秘的矮人遗迹。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2373440/extras/2e82d7e4cd91313530fea5f154635c67.poster.avif?t=1771500911\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2373440/extras/2e82d7e4cd91313530fea5f154635c67.webm?t=1771500911\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2373440/extras/2e82d7e4cd91313530fea5f154635c67.mp4?t=1771500911\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
